::: Install AZOTE on Hyprland :::

1) install these:
$ sudo pacman -S swaybg
$ sudo pacman -S azote

------------------------------------

2) Edit hyprland config:
$ ~/.config/hypr/hyprland.conf

uncomment (or delete!)
# exec-once = wpaperd
add this:
exec-once = ~/.azotebg-hyprland

3) remove (if present):
sudo pacman -R wpaperd
sudo rm -R ~/.config/wpaperd/
